cipated, delivering enhanced comfort and superior views that elevate your entire vacation experience for modest additional investment.<\\/p><p>Your medieval-themed escape awaits at the Magic Excalibur Hotel Benidorm, where legendary hospitality meets modern comfort along Spain\'s most celebrated coastline. Book your enchanting Costa Blanca adventure today and discover why thousands of guests return year after year to this magical destination.<\\/p>\",\"meta_title\":\"Magic Excalibur Hotel Benidorm Spain Stay\",\"slug\":\"magic-excalibur-hotel-benidorm-spain-stay\",\"sort_order\":\"2\",\"meta_keywords\":\"Magic Excalibur Hotel Benidorm, Benidorm hotels, all-inclusive Benidorm, family resorts Spain, Magic Costa Blanca, Benidorm holidays\",\"meta_description\":\"Book Magic Excalibur Hotel Benidorm for a fun family getaway! Enjoy themed rooms, pools, all-inclusive dining, and top-rated entertainment.\",\"canonical_url\":null,\"schema\":null,\"featured_image\":\"uploads\\/1763136662_691754964646c_6.webp\",\"recommended\":0}', '119.73.96.21', 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/142.0.0.0 Safari/537.36', 'https://topcodevoucher.com/admin/blogs/17', 'PUT', '2025-11-14 11:11:02', '2025-11-14 11:11:02'),
